sentences: SBSTA Chair Muyungi proposed a contact group to consider this issue.
Fiji, for the G-77/CHINA, supported by BRAZIL, EGYPT, INDIA, ALGERIA, ARGENTINA and others, opposed, explaining that it had not been previously agreed.
The US, the EU, SWITZERLAND, CANADA, NEW ZEALAND and AUSTRALIA, expressed willingness to discuss this issue and supported a contact group.
SBSTA Chair Muyungi will consult with parties informally and report back to the SBSTA.
The workshop on agriculture will take place as planned.
